      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINNIE RUMBLE (6) had been super consistent recording two placings in a row before she was rewarded with a win last time, scoring at this track over 457m (25.58). Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Hard to go past. FANCIFUL (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 25.53 beating ZEPHYR. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Form should stack up. ZEPHYR (4) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 0.8 lengths from the winner FANCIFUL (25.59) at this track. Must be included in calculations. SHE'S OUR GAL (2) is a surprise last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
